## ğŸ§© Workflow Overview

1. Chat message received
2. Condition check (new / returning user)
3. Initial greeting (if first-time user)
4. AI agent processes the request
5. Tool calls:
   - Create calendar event
   - Get events
   - Append or update Google Sheet
6. Response sent back via webhook

